					&lt;description&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;div style="margin-bottom:20px;"&gt;&lt;img width="1600" height="900" src="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Secure Code Warrior Takes Secure Coding Prowess to New Heights With Missions" loading="lazy" srcset="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions.jpg 1600w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions-300x169.jpg 300w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions-768x432.jpg 768w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New real-world simulations build on developers’ secure coding skills while introducing educational scaffolding Global secure coding company, Secure Code Warrior, has launched Missions—hands-on, interactive coding simulations of real-world applications that encourage developers to experience the real-time impact of poor code practices in a safe environment. Missions is the result of Secure Code Warrior’s acquisition of [&amp;#8230;]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://aithority.com/systems-languages/programming-languages/secure-code-warrior-takes-secure-coding-prowess-to-new-heights-with-missions/"&gt;Secure Code Warrior Takes Secure Coding Prowess to New Heights With Missions&lt;/a&gt; appeared first on &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://aithority.com"&gt;AiThority&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
]]&gt;&lt;/description&gt;
										&lt;content:encoded&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;div style="margin-bottom:20px;"&gt;&lt;img width="1600" height="900" src="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Secure Code Warrior Takes Secure Coding Prowess to New Heights With Missions" loading="lazy" srcset="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions.jpg 1600w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions-300x169.jpg 300w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions-768x432.jpg 768w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Secure-Code-Warrior-Takes-Secure-Coding-Prowess-to-New-Heights-With-Missions-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;header&gt;
&lt;div class="bw-release-subhead"&gt;
&lt;p class="bwalignc"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;i&gt;New real-world simulations build on developers’ secure coding skills while introducing educational scaffolding&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Global secure coding company, Secure Code Warrior, has launched Missions—hands-on, interactive coding simulations of real-world applications that encourage developers to experience the real-time impact of poor code practices in a safe environment. Missions is the result of Secure Code Warrior’s acquisition of Iceland-based start-up Adversary in April 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p id="pull-quote"&gt;Secure Code Warrior is absolutely thrilled to bring you the next level of developer-centric, interactive security training: Missions!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;40 missions covering common security vulnerabilities are currently available, all of which are based on real-world scenarios like the cyber-attacks and &lt;a href="https://aithority.com/?s=security"&gt;security&lt;/a&gt; breaches &lt;a href="https://aithority.com/?s=Facebook"&gt;Facebook&lt;/a&gt;, WhatsApp, &lt;a href="https://aithority.com/?s=GitHub"&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt; and high-profile banks have faced. Targeted at developers, engineering leads and software security professionals, Missions challenges coders to experience these complex issues in a safe environment. This empowers developers to explore different ways to solve each Mission and encourages coders to practice their skills and knowledge, fostering a step-by-step approach to learning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Recommended AI News&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;: &lt;a class="post-url post-title" href="https://aithority.com/robots/automation/saferide-launches-vinsight-a-revolutionary-deep-learning-vehicle-health-management-platform/"&gt;SafeRide Launches vInsight – a Revolutionary Deep-Learning Vehicle Health Management Platform&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pieterdanhieux/"&gt;Pieter Danhieux&lt;/a&gt;, Co-Founder and CEO of Secure Code Warrior, said,&nbsp;“Missions is like a flight simulator for coders. Just like a pilot who needs to continually train to keep flying, Missions offers practical applications of live code in a hyper-relevant environment designed to encourage coders to understand attacks, practice and perfect their secure coding skills and knowledge.”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;“We’re levelling up our existing offerings in a logical fashion and creating a progressive, scaffolded approach to building skills. It helps developers move from merely recalling knowledge to systematically building upon their experiences and skillset in real-time, fostering valuable secure coding skills that are job-relevant and allowing coders to experience the impact of insecure code first hand, in a safe environment,”&nbsp;Danhieux concluded.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Recommended AI News&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;: &lt;a class="post-url post-title" href="https://aithority.com/saas/quark-ai-brings-unsurpassed-accuracy-speed-and-scale-to-enterprise-customer-responsiveness/"&gt;Quark.ai Brings Unsurpassed Accuracy, Speed and Scale To Enterprise Customer Responsiveness&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Secure Code Warrior Missions are included as part of Secure Code Warrior’s standard feature set, with seven language frameworks supported at launch, including Java:Spring, C#(.NET):MVC, C#(.NET):Web Forms, Python:Django, Java:Enterprise Edition (JSP), JavaScript:Node.JS and C#:Core.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Principal Engineer at Optum who has trialled Missions over the past fortnight said,&nbsp;“Missions is a practical, hands-on exercise in identifying, locating and resolving potential security issues. Before this, learning to code securely was a trial and error process. Using real code and frameworks to demonstrate the consequences of insecure code shows engineers why they should work on secure code—all through a fun, interactive game interface.”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For developers interested in taking on the mindset of a security researcher, Secure Code Warrior has released a public mission simulating the Unicode vulnerability that impacted GitHub in 2019.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Recommended AI News&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;: &lt;a class="post-url post-title" href="https://aithority.com/security/trend-micro-integrates-with-aws-gateway-load-balancer-for-improved-security-function/"&gt;Trend Micro Integrates With AWS Gateway Load Balancer for Improved Security Function&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/header&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://aithority.com/systems-languages/programming-languages/secure-code-warrior-takes-secure-coding-prowess-to-new-heights-with-missions/"&gt;Secure Code Warrior Takes Secure Coding Prowess to New Heights With Missions&lt;/a&gt; appeared first on &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://aithority.com"&gt;AiThority&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
