					&lt;description&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;div style="margin-bottom:20px;"&gt;&lt;img width="1600" height="900" src="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Checkmarx Brings Application Security Testing Solutions to AWS Marketplace and Achieves AWS DevOps Competency Status" loading="lazy" srcset="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status.jpg 1600w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status-300x169.jpg 300w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status-768x432.jpg 768w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Listing and designation provide greater flexibility and confidence for organizations seeking to simplify development of secure software Checkmarx, a global leader in software security solutions for DevOps, announced major milestones in its relationship with Amazon Web Services (AWS), bringing its software security solutions to AWS Marketplace and earning AWS DevOps Competency&nbsp;status. With these moves, Checkmarx [&amp;#8230;]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://aithority.com/security/checkmarx-brings-application-security-testing-solutions-to-aws-marketplace/"&gt;Checkmarx Brings Application Security Testing Solutions to AWS Marketplace and Achieves AWS DevOps Competency Status&lt;/a&gt; appeared first on &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://aithority.com"&gt;AiThority&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
