										&lt;content:encoded&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;div style="margin-bottom:20px;"&gt;&lt;img width="1600" height="900" src="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Checkmarx Brings Application Security Testing Solutions to AWS Marketplace and Achieves AWS DevOps Competency Status" loading="lazy" srcset="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status.jpg 1600w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status-300x169.jpg 300w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status-768x432.jpg 768w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Checkmarx-Brings-Application-Security-Testing-Solutions-to-AWS-Marketplace-and-Achieves-AWS-DevOps-Competency-Status-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;i&gt;Listing and designation provide greater flexibility and confidence for organizations seeking to simplify development of secure software&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Checkmarx, a global leader in software security solutions for DevOps, announced major milestones in its relationship with &lt;a href="https://aithority.com/?s=Amazon+Web+Services"&gt;Amazon Web Services&lt;/a&gt; (AWS), bringing its software &lt;a href="https://aithority.com/?s=security+solutions"&gt;security solutions&lt;/a&gt; to AWS Marketplace and earning AWS DevOps Competency&nbsp;status. With these moves, Checkmarx is delivering greater simplicity, flexibility, and confidence to customers looking to deploy application security testing (AST) solutions into their AWS CI/CD pipelines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Checkmarx provides automated solutions that simplify and speed up the process of security testing in fast-paced &lt;a href="https://aithority.com/?s=DevOps"&gt;DevOps&lt;/a&gt; environments. Checkmarx SAST, IAST, SCA, and Codebashing integrate seamlessly with developer workflows and tools to quickly find and remediate vulnerabilities in both custom and open source code before software is released into production. Of note, Checkmarx’s availability in AWS Marketplace follows the company’s recent string of partnership activity with premier software development platforms including&nbsp;&lt;a href="https://aithority.com/?s=DevOps"&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;and&nbsp;GitLab.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Recommended AI News&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;: &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a class="post-url post-title" href="https://aithority.com/computing/ayar-labs-secures-35-million-in-series-b-funding/"&gt;Ayar Labs Secures $35 Million in Series B Funding and Adds New Strategic and Global Investorss&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The AWS DevOps Competency recognizes that Checkmarx provides a proven technology with deep expertise in helping organizations implement application security within continuous integration and delivery practices on AWS. With this latest certification, Checkmarx becomes the only AST solutions provider to possess both the AWS Security and DevOps Competencies, underscoring its commitment to helping organizations move their DevOps initiatives to the cloud.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Recommended AI News&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;: &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a class="post-url post-title" href="https://aithority.com/gaming/banyan-software-announces-acquisition-of-rinknet/"&gt;Banyan Software Announces Acquisition of RinkNet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="text-transform: initial;"&gt;&amp;#8220;Checkmarx empowers cloud-first organizations to enhance the security of the software they release while providing a seamless experience for developers,&amp;#8221; said &lt;a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-nilsson-bb511b2/"&gt;Robert Nilsson&lt;/a&gt;, VP of Product Management, Checkmarx. &amp;#8220;Bringing our solutions to AWS Marketplace, as well as achieving both the AWS Security and DevOps Competencies, demonstrate our dedication to the AWS community and our customers in helping them strategically and securely navigate their cloud and digital transformation journeys.&amp;#8221;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AWS enables scalable, flexible, and cost-effective solutions for banking and payments, capital markets, and insurance organizations, from startups to global enterprises. To support the seamless integration and deployment of these solutions, AWS established the&nbsp;AWS Competency Program&nbsp;to help customers identify AWS Consulting and Technology Partners with deep industry experience and expertise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Recommended AI News&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;: &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a class="post-url post-title" href="https://aithority.com/machine-learning/neural-networks/quantum-computing/coldquanta-raises-32-million-in-series-a-funding/"&gt;ColdQuanta Raises $32 Million in Series A Funding to Accelerate Development of Quantum Systems&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
