					&lt;description&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;div style="margin-bottom:20px;"&gt;&lt;img width="1600" height="900" src="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/JumpCloud-Launches-New-Integrations-with-Slack-Salesforce-GitHub-Atlassian-and-AWS.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="JumpCloud Improves User Identity Lifecycle Management with Slack, Salesforce, GitHub, Atlassian, and AWS Integrations" loading="lazy" srcset="https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/JumpCloud-Launches-New-Integrations-with-Slack-Salesforce-GitHub-Atlassian-and-AWS.jpg 1600w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/JumpCloud-Launches-New-Integrations-with-Slack-Salesforce-GitHub-Atlassian-and-AWS-300x169.jpg 300w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/JumpCloud-Launches-New-Integrations-with-Slack-Salesforce-GitHub-Atlassian-and-AWS-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/JumpCloud-Launches-New-Integrations-with-Slack-Salesforce-GitHub-Atlassian-and-AWS-768x432.jpg 768w, https://aithority.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/JumpCloud-Launches-New-Integrations-with-Slack-Salesforce-GitHub-Atlassian-and-AWS-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;JumpCloud&nbsp;announced new integrations that provide IT admins easier user&nbsp;identity lifecycle management across multiple applications from a single platform. These new integrations with Slack, Salesforce, Atlassian,&nbsp;GitHub, and&nbsp;AWS&nbsp;provide streamlined user management to the most common business applications, reducing the time IT admins spend onboarding and offboarding users from hours to minutes. Recommended AI News: InterDigital and Blacknut [&amp;#8230;]&lt;/p&gt;
